  "title": "MTDeathLocator",
  "description": "A simple way to track back your place of death!",
  "body": "<center>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6409f4531029055889fbe51e\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6408641270e12369ddaa4e0c\" /> <a href=\"https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/%E2%9A%A1-mtdeathlocator-%E2%9A%A1-teammt.96266/updates\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6409f42c1029055889fbe51c\" />  </a> <a href=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/wiki/MTDeathLocator\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6409f4291029055889fbe51a\" />  </a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6409f4261029055889fbe518\" />  </a>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/699fa66bae527b67c278e465\" />\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\">  <img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/638a91e9aa2989386ab8ef79\" />  </a>\n\n</center>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Full Transcript</summary>\n\nVANILLA FRIENDLY\nThe plugin keeps a simple interface, and doesn't disrupt the vanilla experience!\nThe plugin offers two ways of finding your last place of death! Teleport and chat coordinates!\n\nCUSTOMIZABLE\nEvery aspect is configurable, without being overloaded!\n\nThis plugin integrates the fully customizable messages protocol. Send clickable components, make chat menus, send URL's and more!\n</details>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/views/HiQtAg4AIT8sDA4YPAIVGxM5JhcxBgEYO1AtAh8YJgouCgEY\" />",
